<A>__{swana inspects herself briefly in the hall mirror, proceeds into the living room. living room swana's apartment leon is pacing up and down. swana enters.}
<C>__{swana}
<D>__{leon, darling, how nice! have you ordered tea or a cocktail?}
<C>__{leon}
<D>__{no thanks, swana.}
<C>__{swana}
